serverlist (Lvl. 0, Opers only)
-----------------------------------------
Syntax:  serverlist [sort] [pattern]
Desc.:   Lists connected servers, sort parameters are :
   -n : sort by numeric, -h : sort by last part of servername
   -u : unsorted (the default)
Examples:
   serverlist
      Displays all connected servers
   serverlist -n *.uk.*
      Displays all connected uk servers, ordered by numeric.
